	The following example creates a label and gives it text:

	```haxe
	var label = new Label();
	label.text = "Hello World";
	this.addChild(label);
	```

	@see [Tutorial: How to use the Label component](https://feathersui.com/learn/haxe-openfl/label/)

	@since 1.0.0
**/
